<div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">

<h1 style="margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)" class="wp-block-post-title">farewell!</h1></div>


<div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content has-small-font-size has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>The CMPI team has ended in 2025.</strong> <strong>Members are still active within CIIL at <a href="https://www.ciil.fr/teams/grassart-mechanobiology-of-host-microbe-interactions" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">MoHMi</a> team and <a href="https://www.ciil.fr/facilities/bfm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">BFM</a> unit facility.</strong></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">We&#8217;re developing an <strong>interdisciplinary</strong> approach combining bacterial genetics, microbiology, cell and molecular biology, biochemistry and biophysics to investigate how pathogens interact with the host cell surface, how the cell responds to this attack and how pathogens subvert this response. The aim is to identify new therapeutic targets and to design new tools in order to inhibit infection.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can navigate here the different <a href="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/?page_id=13" data-type="page" data-id="13">research</a> topics carried out by the lab <a href="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/?page_id=49" data-type="page" data-id="49">members</a>, the associated <a href="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/?page_id=19" data-type="page" data-id="19">publications</a>, the different <a href="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/?page_id=21" data-type="page" data-id="21">teaching</a> activities we&#8217;re involved in, the <a href="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/?page_id=433" data-type="page" data-id="433">press</a> releases, and how to <a href="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/?page_id=22" data-type="page" data-id="22">contact</a> us.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border is-style-default"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="320" height="320" data-id="573" src="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/12102020_20001_XbackYgo_0001CH1_CROP2FINAL.gif.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-573" style="border-radius:10px"/></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border is-style-default"><img decoding="async" width="256" height="256" data-id="585" src="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Supplementary-movie-4.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-585" style="border-radius:10px"/></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border is-style-default"><img decoding="async" width="159" height="164" data-id="594" src="https://cmpi.cnrs.fr/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/IP-Create_Image_Subset-24_AdobeExpress.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-594" style="border-radius:10px"/></figure>
</figure>



<div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group is-content-justification-space-between is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-73d85c4d wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
